summary: Complex Ornate Retexture Of The Dwarven Armor Set.
descriptionHtml:
Description:

This is the first mod that I upload to this page, this means that I\'ve previously made other retexture mods but they were only used by myself.
I simply made an ornate retexture of the dwarven armor set using the program Paint.net, easier than Photoshop but with a lot o nice features. It took me about ten hours to do it (not in a row) so I hope you enjoy it!

Installation:

-Download the .RAR file.
-Extract the Data folder into your Skyrim folder.
-Yes to replace.
-Play Skyrim and enjoy it!

Unistallation:

-Delete the 4 files usually located at Program files\\The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\armor\\dwarven\\m
